      <title>World’s Largest Auto Glass Maker Fuyao Group Sees Founder Cao Dewang Step Down as Chairman</title>
      <link>https://technode.com/2025/10/16/worlds-largest-auto-glass-maker-fuyao-group-sees-founder-cao-dewang-step-down-as-chairman/</link>
      <dc:creator><![CDATA[TechNode Feed]]></dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Oct 2025 10:27:10 +0000</pubDate>
