s (up to RMB 10,000 / $1,380), quantities, delivery methods, and shipping fees, with a [&#8230;]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure><img width="1024" height="683" src="https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?fit=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-rss-image-size size-rss-image-size wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=780%2C520&amp;ssl=1 780w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=400%2C267&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?resize=706%2C471&amp;ssl=1 706w, https://i0.wp.com/technode.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/leone-venter-mTkXSSScrzw-unsplash.jpg?fit=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1&amp;w=370 370w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" /></figure>
<p>Chinese lifestyle platform Xiaohongshu, also known as Rednote, is testing a new “Quick Sell” feature that lets users list secondhand items directly under posts or share product cards in private chats, according to <em>Tech Planet</em>. Users can set item names, prices (up to RMB 10,000 / $1,380), quantities, delivery methods, and shipping fees, with a 0.6% transaction fee similar to that of Xianyu, a used goods e-commerce platform operated by Alibaba.</p>



<p>The feature expands Rednote’s push into e-commerce. The company merged its e-commerce and livestreaming units in 2023 to form a standalone commerce division and added a “Marketplace” tab to its app this year to promote shopping and live-selling content. [<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/rfUeaEcK0isUXNOBBT6Y0A">Tech Planet</a>, in Chinese]</p>
]]></content:encoded>
